    },
    {
      "id": "69ac3e7f7838e30000001132f1",
      "text": "[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772895855,
      "updated": 1772895879
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac3eb40000000000e18b2a",
      "text": "\tオーケストレーションやってみたい",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772895909,
      "updated": 1772895923
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac3ea20000000000e18b28",
      "text": "\t\t生成AIに対する評価をしなおしたい",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772895891,
      "updated": 1772897534
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac44ff0000000000827de8",
      "text": "\tAIに要約させた情報もまあ悪くはないんだけど",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772897536,
      "updated": 1772897548
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac450c0000000000827de9",
      "text": "\t　専門サイトの長くて細かい文章からしか得られない栄養もある",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772897548,
      "updated": 1772897573
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac452f0000000000827dea",
      "text": "\t　今は[肩中兪]（けんちゅうゆ）について調べてたとこ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772897583,
      "updated": 1772897597
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac453d0000000000827deb",
      "text": "\t　　https://beauty.hotpepper.jp/kr/slnH000535975/blog/bidA099298296.html",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772897597,
      "updated": 1772897611
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac457f0000000000827ded",
      "text": "\t　https://hbtoyama.com/blog/2023/07/3382",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772897663,
      "updated": 1772897666
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac46040000000000827def",
      "text": "\t　肩・首周りの[ツボ押し]について調べてるけど奥が深い",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772897800,
      "updated": 1772897818
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac461b0000000000827df0",
      "text": "\t　　ていうか人間の身体のメンテムズすぎだろ問題",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772897819,
      "updated": 1772897835
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac46340000000000827df1",
      "text": "\t　　こりゃあ医療含めて無くならない訳ですな",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772897845,
      "updated": 1772897855
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac46840000000000827df2",
      "text": "\t　[淵腋]（えんえき）もいいね",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772897924,
      "updated": 1772897975
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac46b70000000000827df3",
      "text": "\t　　https://co2chi.com/blog/staff/%ef%bd%8e-%e5%90%89%e7%94%b0/%e8%ba%ab%e4%bd%93%e3%82%92%e4%bc%b8%e3%81%b0%e3%81%97%e3%81%a6%e6%b0%97%e6%8c%81%e3%81%a1%e3%82%92%e8%bb%bd%e3%81%8f%e3%80%9c%e6%b7%b5%e8%85%8b%e3%81%ae%e3%81%a4%e3%81%bc%e3%80%9c/",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772897975,
      "updated": 1772897976
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac46b80000000000827df4",
      "text": "   撫でるか軽い力で押す程度が良さそうだけど",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772897976,
      "updated": 1772898009
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac49680000000000827dfb",
      "text": "  [足ツボ]考えたやつマジで狂ってる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772898665,
      "updated": 1772898674
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac47f50000000000827df5",
      "text": " とにかくやる気でないやつ、ただ体の巡りが良くない説ちょっとある",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772898293,
      "updated": 1772898316
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac48440000000000827df8",
      "text": " 　他にも睡眠不足栄養不足疲労とか可能性考えたらきりないけど",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772898372,
      "updated": 1772898390
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac48550000000000827df9",
      "text": " 　　`$ my health test`とかで一発確認できないの不便",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772898390,
      "updated": 1772898435
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac48950000000000827dfa",
      "text": " 　　[myコマンド]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772898454,
      "updated": 1772898458
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac480b0000000000827df6",
      "text": " 　てのひらの指の付け根部分とかを揉んでる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772898316,
      "updated": 1772898348
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac483e0000000000827df7",
      "text": " 　なんかね、脳みそだけ良くしても他の身体の部位は無視できないんだなって",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772898367,
      "updated": 1772898575
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac49b50000000000827dfc",
      "text": " 足裏揉んでたらじんじんきた",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772898741,
      "updated": 1772898751
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac49ca0000000000827dfe",
      "text": " 　両手親指でグッグッグッってしてただけなのに",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772898762,
      "updated": 1772898776
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac3e7f7838e30000001bbc4e",
